iSticky iPad [and iPhone:orientation] sticky footer

An experiment in how it might be possible to target devices using media queries. 

http://mashcode.github.com/iSticky/

* HTML template contains css for iPad sticky footer. Thanks to Ryan Fait http://ryanfait.com 
* Uses css @media queries to point iphone, ipad and "all" other formats to unique stylesheets. 
* Stickiness is disabled in non-ipad devices.


